"@type": "HowToStep"
,"text": "Make the topping: Mix yogurt, condensed milk, Mexican crema, and vanilla together in a bowl until well combined."
} ,{
"@type": "HowToStep"
,"text": "Make the fruit salads: Divide cantaloupe, papaya, apple, and banana among 4 individual bowls, arranging each fruit in its own section. Place strawberries in the center of each bowl. Sprinkle granola, raisins, and coconut over the bowls, then drizzle with the topping."
} ]
